        <h1>WELCOME TO GLOBAL HARVEST LABS </h1>
        <p>Global Harvest Laboratories is a leader in providing   strategic services to the pharmaceutical, biotechnological, medical   equipment, and diagnostic equipment industries.<br />
        <br />
          We specialize in   identifying opportunities to help your company better develop,   manufacture, distribute and promote drug products within emerging global   markets.<br />
          <br />
        Whether through our network of partners, or research   and development labs in US, China and Japan, Global Harvest Pharma has the industry   experience to understand your company’s unique issues and the tools to   help you grow your business.</p>
